data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. VA ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AVAILABLE TO THOSE THAT QUALIFY at a 3.25% INTEREST RATE. Elevated Home MINUTES to the GULF of MEXICO offering (2) bedrooms, (2) bathrooms upstairs PLUS a downstairs apartment vibe (NOT included in the sq. footage you see) that features a living room, (1) bedroom, and (1) bathroom. Feels like a daily V-A-C-A-T-I-O-N here and the BACKYARD will blow your mind! It’s been carefully crafted with a Zen Bamboo Garden, countless plants, trees, shrubs, and plants nestled throughout, hand-made beach area and secondary leisure area covered with seashells boasting a hammock. The bamboo garden has several varieties of bamboo including Buddha Belly Bamboo. River Rock and Pea Gravel beds, natural stone, wood borders, solar lights and hanging plants throughout. ITEMS WORTHY OF MENTION; Oversized 1-car garage, Roof (2022), Full Interior paint (2022/2023), (3) coats to second-floor balcony (2023), NEW laminate flooring (living room & owner's suite), Garbage Disposal (2023), Stainless-Steel Microwave & Dishwasher (2023), Updated stainless-steel kitchen refrigerator & stove, Washer & Dryer (2023), HVAC coil system (2022), Water Softener, Boat Dock & Dock Light painted (2023), Shed, 3-Fuel Outdoor Grill & Smoker (charcoal/propane gas/electric), garage includes refrigerator & workstation, removal of all popcorn ceiling (2022), Bottom porch painted (2023), NEW ceiling fans and FRONT & BACKYARD MAKEOVER (2022). The home pours out natural light! (2) sets of French doors to wrap around porch. Cathedral ceiling, with dual ceiling fans, and large windows. AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST; floorplans, survey, elevation certificate, video, features & upgrade sheet, & list of plants/trees. Golf cart your way right over to Ollie Oysters for some seafood and music, take sunset at Sam’s Beach Bar, or stroll alone to have some time to rest for yourself. NO deed restrictions. The owner is moving to Costa Rica and says the entire home can come furnished and the boat out back is for sale. You can fish right off the back dock and find Red fish, Sheepshead, Mackerel, Grouper and Blue Crabs. FLOOD INSURANCE IS ASSUMABLE.  Buy a Little Piece of Florida Now!
